# Instantiated as the repo-root `.dockerignore` (stored here without the leading
# dot, like the other scaffold dotfiles). The build context is the repo root, so
# this keeps the image small and avoids leaking local secrets/caches into layers.
# Adapt on fork to the app's stack (drop the Python or Node lines as appropriate).

.git
.github

# Node
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo

# Python
.venv
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc

# Local dev / secrets — never bake into an image
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.mise.local.toml
.claude

# Test + coverage output
**/coverage
**/.pytest_cache
**/*.log
